Name: SourceLanguage
Description: The language of the original transform (e.g., SPSS, SAS, Stata, R)

Name: SourceFileName
Description: The name of the file that contained the original transform code

Name: SourceStartIndex
Description: The character index of the beginning of the transform code

Name: SourceStopIndex
Description: The character index of the end of the transform code

Name: SourceText
Description: The original source code of the data transform code
